lote-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-ingredients\"\u003eIngredients\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCorn\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eMayo\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eSour cream\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eCotija cheese\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eChili powder\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eLime\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eCilantro\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/elote-recipe/?tp_image_id=137827\" data-pin-title=\"Elotes\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-recipe.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-how-to-make-elote\"\u003eHow to make Elote\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn a large pot, bring enough water to submerge the corn to a boil. Salt the water. As the water heats, shuck the corn, removing the husk (leaves) and silk threads. Boil the corn for 10 minutes. Then drain and pat dry.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn a small bowl, stir together the mayo and sour cream. On a large plate, combine the cotija and chili powder. Coat the corn with the mayo mixture, then roll in the cheese mixture. Alternatively, you could sprinkle the cheese mixture over the corn once you’ve added the mayo mixture.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eAfter plating, sprinkle cilantro over the top and serve with fresh lime wedges. I also sometimes add a little hot sauce too, but this is optional.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/elote-recipe/?tp_image_id=137828\" data-pin-title=\"Elotes\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1200px) 730px, (min-width: 1080px) 650px, (min-width: 1024px) 630px, calc(100vw - 40px)\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201200%201200\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-lazy-srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-156x156.jpg 156w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-288x288.jpg 288w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients-500x500.jpg 500w\" data-lazy-src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/elote-ingredients.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"h-tips-amp-notes\"\u003eTips \u0026amp; Notes\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSimilar to Parmesan, sometimes Cotija is sold by the block/sphere and sometimes it’s sold powdery. I like to buy it in its powdery form for this Elote recipe, but if you can only find it whole simply finely grate before using.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eTo add even more flavors, you can swap the chili powder for \u003ca href=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/taco-seasoning-recipe/\"\u003etaco seasoning\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eIf you are using canned corn instead of fresh on-the-cob corn, simply drain from the can and heat on the stove top. Once hot, remove from the heat and stir in the other ingredients. I reserve half the cheese and cilantro to sprinkle over the top for a pretty presentation.\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eElote leftovers can be stored in an airtight container in the refrigerator for at least 3 days. \u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1200\" height=\"1200\" data-pin-url=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/elote-recipe/?tp_image_id=137829\" data-pin-title=\"Elotes\" src=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes.jpg 1200w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes-300x300.jpg 300w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes-1024x1024.jpg 1024w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes-150x150.jpg 150w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes-768x768.jpg 768w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes-100x100.jpg 100w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes-60x60.jpg 60w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes-750x750.jpg 750w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes-730x730.jpg 730w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes-700x700.jpg 700w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/how-to-make-elotes-550x550.jpg 550w, https://abeautifulmess.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/